				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">1. do ldon takish adventures, and purchase the diamond prism of championship, approx 760 takish points.
<br />
2. put one of the four mage focus items (torch of alna, stein of ulissa, etc) in an inventory slot.
<br />
3. memorize rathe's son.
<br />
4. get quick summoning 2.
<br />
5. get a spell haste item, whether that be your summoned ring or another item.
<br />

<br />
congrats!  you are now progressing down the pet canni path of ultimate mana regeneration!  of course, there are some better options out there that are a bit ways from you... potime focus, for example.  but for now, the above five should make a big difference in your pet canni skills...
<br />

<br />
-cc
<br />
magelo: 10393</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
