				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm sure this is repeat of stuff others have already said but:
<br />

<br />
1) Specialize in Conjuration
<br />

<br />
2) Get max mana preservation possible per pet
<br />
......-Swirling cloak of the elements Summoning efficiency IV Item (wet dream ?nonexistant? drop from named giant in PoS Forrest Fort) 
<br />
......-Elemental Seeves of the prime
<br />
......-Any other of many mana preservation items in game.
<br />

<br />
3) Maximize speed of casting
<br />
......-Purchase: AA Quick Summoning III (or quicksummoning II and Summoning Haste IV item)
<br />
......-Buff with Blessing of Reverence
<br />

<br />
4) Maximize pet hitpoints (GoDS, Diamond Prism of Companionship, etc. etc.)
<br />

<br />
5) Get AA skill suspend minion II and Hot key
<br />

<br />
6) Get Insta Clickie "reclaim energy" item (ie.- Stien of Ulysssia / Torch or Alna / etc.) and put in hot key 
<br />

<br />
7) Mem Rathe's Son and hot key
<br />

<br />

<br />
Then you are set...
<br />
Just suspend pet (with warning to group that you are doing so), and start alternating between hot keys to cast earth pet and inta reclaim.  Then unsuspend pet when FM.
<br />

<br />
-Meldor</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
