			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">65 Earth pet unbuffed = 4800 HP
<br />
DPoC focused 65 Earth = 5250 HP
<br />
GoDS focused 65 Earth = (something like 5600, don't remember exactly, but its more then the DPoC and less then ASoS)
<br />
ASoS focused 65 Earth = 6200 HP
<br />

<br />
so... 
<br />

<br />
no focus&lt;&lt;DPoC&lt;&lt;GoDS&lt;&lt;ASoS
<br />

<br />
Doing canni with 65 Earth, no pet-focus, SCM3, Spec Conj 200, Mana Pres IV and 5 second pet is about 135 mana/tic regen.  All the same but with DPoC comes out to around 170 mana/tic regen.  Using ASoS and the best mana savings focus out there will net you around 260 mana/tic regen doing canni.  Canni with all that and the GoDS is somewhere between 170 and 260 per tic.<br />_________________<br /><Center><b><a href= "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=36994">Sage Eandori Raintree</a></b>
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Solusek Ro Server</span>
<br />
</center></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
