				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Works at level 49 with earth pet, and I think at 50 is a little better with monster pet (has a few more hps).
<br />

<br />
As you gain AA, pet focus, mana pres gear .. you watch the blue bar go up faster.
<br />

<br />
Make sure to have a mana pres item for all levels, or your efficiency as a whole will be dented.
<br />

<br />
Oh, and make sure you have a clicky Reclaim Energy item to speed up the process and save a spell slot.<br />_________________<br />-- I used to be an atheist until I became an Arch Convoker --</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Ducalio on Thu Dec 04, 2003 2:38 pm; edited 1 time in total</span></td>
